Text: Enron Astroworld TicketsEnron announces UNLIMITED discounted AstroWorld tickets for employees Due to overwhelming employee feedback we have negotiated unlimited discounted AstroWorld tickets for you and your family in place of the traditional Enron Day At AstroWorld We hope this will allow Enron families to plan their funfilled summer trips to AstroWorld at their own convenience Enron AstroWorld tickets are Retail which includes admission for one plus a meal ticket to one of five restaurants at AstroWorld Six Flags AstroWorld is a worldclass family entertainment complex filled with exciting rides and attractions including heartpounding coasters over blockbuster shows interactive street entertainers and starstudded concerts Enron families will be able to purchase unlimited tickets for use anytime during the season Tickets will be on sale at Enrons Federal Credit Union EB Visit the credit union in person to make your purchases AstroWorld tickets will not be mailed Enron employees who are not already Enron FCU members may pay by cash or money order only All Enron Employees are encouraged to take advantage of this great summer fun deal and may purchase tickets through August th
